div1.p:
Court. (to the Prisoner,
Eleanor Keith
) In the first Place, what have you to say for yourself ?

Q. (to
Thomas Thornhill
) What do you know of this Matter?

Simson. Please you, my Lord, I have known the Prisoner (
Elizabeth Jones
) these sixteen Years, and have lodg'd with her four Years within a Trifle.

Evans. She shew'd me one Shilling, as she could not put it off; but she did not know how she (
Susannah Jones
) put off so many.
